.TH "VISUALVIEWPORT.WIDTH" "3JS" "September 15, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
VisualViewport.width \- VisualViewport: width property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]width\f[B]\f[R] read\-only property of the
\f[CR]VisualViewport\f[R] interface returns the width of the visual
viewport, in CSS pixels, or \f[CR]0\f[R] if current document is not
fully active.
.SH VALUE
A double.
